--- Pacifix / Swoop---

Pacifix turns to face Grimlock, an annoyed glint appears in his eye 
as he looks up to meet the taller bot's steady gaze, "Grimlock, I 
am the leader of this mission. Get you, and your Dinobots onto the 
ship." He turns his head to Ironhide, with a can-you-convince-him-
we-need-to-leave look on his face.

Swoop squawks quietly, "Grimlock should be leader of Autobot 
mission..."
